---
import {Image} from 'astro:assets'
import heroImage from '../../assets/images/heroimg.png'
import Button from '../common/Button.astro'
import Capsule from '../common/Capsule.astro'
import CircleCheck from '../icons/CircleCheck.astro'
---
<section class="hero section-container">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <Capsule>Nueva Línea Premium</Capsule>
      <h1>
        Inspiramos bienestar, transformamos vidas
      </h1>
      <p>En un mundo que avanza con velocidad, elegimos el valor del equilibrio.
Así nace térbol I Inspira: una invitación a vivir más y vivir mejor, desde la ciencia, la conciencia y la excelencia.</p>

      <Button variant='primary' size='md' class='full'>REGISTRARME COMO PROMOTORA</Button>
      <Button variant='primary' size='sm' class='compact'>REGISTRARME COMO PROMOTORA</Button>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <CircleCheck/>
          Respaldo científico
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <CircleCheck/>
          Alta gama
        </div><div class="feature">
          <CircleCheck/>
          Modelo B2C
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="picture">
      <Image 
        src={heroImage} 
        alt="Hero image" 
        width={800} 
        class="hero-img" 
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>

  .hero {
    padding-top: 100px;
  }

  .compact {
    display: none;
  }
  .container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    align-self: stretch;
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .content {
    display: flex;
    width: 825px;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  h1 {
    color: var(--text-blue-900);
    font-size: 100px;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 100%; 
  }

  .content p {
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .picture {
    display: flex;
    width: 502px;
    height: 446px;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-width: 400px;
  }

  .hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .features {
    display: flex;
    align-items: start;
    justify-content: start;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .container {
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .container {
    flex-direction: column;
    }

    .content {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .picture {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features {
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .picture {
      min-width: inherit;
      aspect-ratio: 3/2;
      height: 100%;
      width: auto;
    }

    .compact {
      display: flex;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .full {
      display: none;
    }

  }

</style>
